snippet.title: SOULCALIBUR VI PSX Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Perhaps it was fate...a tale of souls and swords. Watch the brand new PSX gameplay trailer for SOULCALIBUR VI featuring Mitsurugi and Sophitia locked in a heroic battle!
